{"type":null,"faqId":45534,"title":"荣耀小K二维码扫描一直在初始化","answer":"<p><span lang=\"EN-US\">1.<span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 7pt; font-stretch: normal\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span>如果小<span lang=\"EN-US\">K</span>上的时间一直不更新，需要确认<span lang=\"EN-US\">SIM</span>卡业务是否正常<span lang=\"EN-US\"><?xml:namespace prefix = o /><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p class=\"ItemListText\"><b><span style=\"COLOR: rgb(255,0,1)\">非常重要：</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p class=\"ItemListText\"><b><span style=\"COLOR: #ff0001\" lang=\"EN-US\">SIM</span></b><b><span style=\"COLOR: rgb(255,0,1)\">卡需开通【</span><span style=\"COLOR: #ff0001\" lang=\"EN-US\">2G</span></b><b><span style=\"COLOR: rgb(255,0,1)\">数据流量业务】、【短信业务】及【来电显示业务】）。</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p class=\"ItemListText\"><b><span style=\"COLOR: rgb(255,0,1)\">深圳及部分地区</span><span style=\"COLOR: #ff0001\" lang=\"EN-US\">2G</span></b><b><span style=\"COLOR: rgb(255,0,1)\">数据业务默认不开通，需要用户拨打</span><span style=\"COLOR: #ff0001\" lang=\"EN-US\">10086</span></b><b><span style=\"COLOR: rgb(255,0,1)\">开通。</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p class=\"ItemListText\"><b><span style=\"COLOR: #ff0001\" lang=\"EN-US\">10086</span></b><b><span style=\"COLOR: rgb(255,0,1)\">电话沟通话术：</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p class=\"ItemListText\"><b><span style=\"COLOR: rgb(255,0,1)\">告知</span><span style=\"COLOR: #ff0001\" lang=\"EN-US\">10086SIM</span></b><b><span style=\"COLOR: rgb(255,0,1)\">卡放在手机上可以上网，但放在儿童电话手表上无法上网，儿童智能手表只支持</span><span style=\"COLOR: #ff0001\" lang=\"EN-US\">2G</span></b><b><span style=\"COLOR: rgb(255,0,1)\">上网，请</span><span style=\"COLOR: #ff0001\" lang=\"EN-US\">10086</span></b><b><span style=\"COLOR: rgb(255,0,1)\">帮忙开通上网功能。</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p class=\"ItemStep\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">2.<span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 7pt; font-stretch: normal\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span>确认手表版本，若手表软件版本为<span lang=\"EN-US\">1.35.4.X</span>以下版本，请用户通过花粉论坛指导帖一键升级至<span lang=\"EN-US\">1.35.4.X</span>版本后再进行配对。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p class=\"ItemListText\">一键升级指导链接：<span lang=\"EN-US\">http://cn.club.vmall.com/thread-6620036-1-1.html<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p class=\"ItemStep\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">3.<span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 7pt; font-stretch: normal\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span>若是刚插入<span lang=\"EN-US\">SIM</span>卡扫描二维码，则需要长按手表侧键<span lang=\"EN-US\">10s</span>重启手表，重启以后等待几分钟，待手表时间准确后方能扫描二维码。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p class=\"ItemStep\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">4.<span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 7pt; font-stretch: normal\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span>若以上步骤均尝试过仍无法扫描，请用户反馈<span lang=\"EN-US\">IMEI</span>号，研发定位。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b>确认业务是否开通正确方法：</b><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p class=\"ItemList\"><span style=\"POSITION: relative; FONT-FAMILY: Wingdings; FONT-SIZE: 8pt; TOP: -1pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Wingdings; mso-bidi-font-family: Wingdings; mso-text-raise: 1.0pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">l<span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 7pt; font-stretch: normal\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span>请确认手表<span lang=\"EN-US\">SIM</span>卡里的短信功能是否正常：可以将<span lang=\"EN-US\">SIM</span>卡放在手机里尝试是否可以收发短信，建议致电<span lang=\"EN-US\">SIM</span>卡运营商客服确认短信收发业务开通 。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p class=\"ItemList\"><span style=\"POSITION: relative; FONT-FAMILY: Wingdings; FONT-SIZE: 8pt; TOP: -1pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Wingdings; mso-bidi-font-family: Wingdings; mso-text-raise: 1.0pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">l<span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 7pt; font-stretch: normal\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span>请确认<span lang=\"EN-US\">SIM</span>卡是否开通了<span lang=\"EN-US\">2G</span>数据流量业务： 由于手表使用的是<span lang=\"EN-US\">2G</span>网络，建议直接拨打<span lang=\"EN-US\">10086</span>开通<span lang=\"EN-US\">2G GPRS</span>数据业务（注：深圳及部分地区<span lang=\"EN-US\">2G</span>数据业务默认不开通，需联系运营商开通<span lang=\"EN-US\">)<o:p></o:p></span></p>","faqTypeId":212,"faqType":"其他","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"1055","faqTypeCode":"Wearable_Device-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1442559368000,"seriesProductName":"K1-G01","visitedTimes":81,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"K1-G01,荣耀小K,儿童手表,K1,二维码,扫描,初始化","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}